dict.string: Today is 42 days, which are six weeks, of the Omer.
Hoy es cuarenta y dos días, que son seis semanas del Omer.
Aujourd'hui est quarante-deux jours, qui sont six semaines du Omer
СЕГОДНЯ СОРОК ДВА ДНЯ - ЧТО СОСТАВЛЯЕТ ШЕСТЬ НЕДЕЛЬ - ОМЕРА.
הַיּוֹם שְׁנַֽיִם וְאַרְבָּעִים יוֹם שֶׁהֵם שִׁשָּׁה שָׁבוּעוֹת לָעֽוֹמֶר
Bonding must enhance a person's nobility. It should nurture and strengthen your own dignity and the dignity of the one with whom you bond.
Emphasize and highlight the strengths of the one with whom you bond.
Does my bonding inhibit the expression of my personality and qualities?
Does it overwhelm the one with whom I bond?
